OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHouseholds in debt         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftime-bomb, says Citizens   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FAdvice                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Fears of a "debt time-bomb" have been  
OL,6, raised by Citizens Advice, which said  
OL,7, growing numbers of households faced a  
OL,8, "wild west" when seeking help.         
OL,10,FThe charity said it is helping more    
OL,11,Fpeople who do not have enough income to
OL,12,Fcover essential expenses.              
OL,14,FDirector of policy Matt Upton said 51% 
OL,15,Fof those it sees with debt issues have 
OL,16,Fnegative budgets, compared with 36%    
OL,17,Fbefore the pandemic.                   
OL,19,FMr Upton said there was no sign of that
OL,20,Ffigure coming down.                    
